The paper deals with improving the performance of long-range wireless communications, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the issue of collisions, which is a security concern and falls under the sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper proposes algorithms to improve the overall throughput of LoRa, which is a topic that falls under the sub-category of Multimedia (cs.MM).
